Maths
Class Matrix

java.lang.Object
  Maths.AbstractMatrix
      Maths.Matrix

public class Matrix
extends AbstractMatrix

Implementation of AbstractMatrix as Default implementation. Uses an 2D array to store the Matrix internal. Should not be used with large matrizes.

Author:
sebastianzillessen
